data.description: MOVE IN READY in a gated community! Beautiful 2 bedroom townhouse with a Den which can be a 3rd bedroom. Master bathroom was just remolded in June. HVAC is from 2020 and kitchen appliances are from 2022. Kings Mill will be repainting the building and putting on a new roof this year. Water is included in the HOA fees. Easy access to the community pool. Minutes from Route 60 shopping. Be sure to check it out before its gone! SELLER IS VERY MOTIVATED!
